<plot>Our hero, a young guy is caught between two worlds: A dream world, where he is living a nice, tidy existence with a beautiful girlfriend, and a dark night-world in which he's being approached only by the images of his TV. The link between these two worlds are his attempts at achieving love or emotion through technology. As we follow him on both sides, it all culminates in a creepy twist that shocks our main character and provokes his temper.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?054568</url></doc>
